---
// src/components/HowItWorks.astro
---
<section class="section">
  <h2 class="text-center">How It <span class="text-thread">Works</span></h2>
  <p class="text-ash text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">Three steps to your personal AI assistant.</p>
  <div class="thread-rail space-y-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="relative">
      <span class="thread-node"></span>
      <span class="timestamp">Step 1</span>
      <h3 class="mb-2">Create Your Agent</h3>
      <p class="text-ash text-sm">Choose a template or start from scratch. Set your language and preferred channels.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="relative">
      <span class="thread-node"></span>
      <span class="timestamp">Step 2</span>
      <h3 class="mb-2">Connect Channels</h3>
      <p class="text-ash text-sm">Link WhatsApp, Android, or Web. Your AI now lives where you communicate.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="relative">
      <span class="thread-node"></span>
      <span class="timestamp">Step 3</span>
      <h3 class="mb-2">Start Chatting</h3>
      <p class="text-ash text-sm">Your AI remembers everything – preferences, tasks, and past conversations.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>